ams</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/John_Trevor_(speaker)" title="John Trevor (speaker)">John Trevor</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Henry_Powle" title="Henry Powle">Henry Powle</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Paul_Foley_(ironmaster)" title="Paul Foley (ironmaster)">Paul Foley</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sir_Thomas_Littleton,_3rd_Baronet" title="Sir Thomas Littleton, 3rd Baronet">Thomas Littleton</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Robert_Harley,_1st_Earl_of_Oxford_and_Earl_Mortimer" title="Robert Harley, 1st Earl of Oxford and Earl Mortimer">Robert Harley</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/John_Smith_(Chancellor_of_the_Exchequer)" title="John Smith (Chancellor of the Exchequer)">John Smith</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Richard_Onslow,_1st_Baron_Onslow" title="Richard Onslow, 1st Baron Onslow">Richard Onslow</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/William_Bromley_(Speaker)" title="William Bromley (Speaker)" class="mw-redirect">William Bromley</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Thomas_Hanmer_(politician)" title="Thomas Hanmer (politician)" class="mw-redirect">Thomas Hanmer</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Spencer_Compton,_1st_Earl_of_Wilmington" title="Spencer Compton, 1st Earl of Wilmington">Spencer Compton</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Arthur_Onslow" title="Arthur Onslow">Arthur Onslow</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/John_Cust" title="John Cust" class="mw-redirect">John Cust</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Fletcher_Norton,_1st_Baron_Grantley" title="Fletcher Norton, 1st Baron Grantley">Fletcher Norton</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a h